name: Pullsh 1.0
body:
First release of Pullsh! Go share memo/note with it.

Create a push or a pull of memo by swiping the action button to left or right.

By pushing a memo, it will be saved on [cloud](https://jienan.xyz/m), and can be accessed with the id you just got.

By pulling a memo, well, you can do that in the this Android app, on the [cloud](https://jienan.xyz/m).
